      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><|channel>thought\n<channel|>It's not really a \"new chapter\" though. That's what people say to make it sound better, but it doesn't feel new. It feels empty. Like the light just went out and there's no point in pretending the bulb is still working. How can it be a new chapter when the main character is already gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
